It&#8217;s all systems go for the payment of social grants to millions of South Africans from today, after Social Development Minister Bathabile Dlamini reassured beneficiaries that grants will be paid by Monday. South Africa Social Security Agency (Sassa ) recipients can look forward to withdrawing their cash today from any ATM across the country, as social grants will continue to made available in the same way.For the full story get a copy of the Dispatch or subscribe to our e-Edition for the complete newspaper with jobs, classifieds, crosswords, TV schedules and back editions